* Spark UI\nDiagnostics
** Access
***_ Cluster page
***_ Spark UI tab
** Jobs Timeline
***_ Execution sequence
***_ Failing jobs (red)
***_ Long-running jobs
***_ Execution gaps
** Failing Jobs
***_ Red status indicator
***_ View failed stage
***_ Specific failure reason
** Long-Running Jobs
***_ Extended duration
***_ Drill into stages
***_ Identify bottlenecks
** Execution Gaps
***_ Normal: short gaps
***_ >1 min gap = driver issue
** Task-Level Metrics
***_ Input / Output
***_ Shuffle Read / Write
***_ Few tasks = low parallelism
***_ Uneven durations = skew
@endmindmap
